  "introduction": {
    "aboutTitle": "About Me",
    "aboutContent_dataScience": "I am a software developer with a recent focus on Data Science. I have worked with .NET, SQL Server and automations, but in 2025 I started a formal transition toward data analysis and modeling. I have explored real challenges such as the WiDS 2022 datathon (breast cancer detection) and WiDS 2025 (ADHD detection in women). I am currently training in various data science tools with the goal of building complete end-to-end projects by early 2026. My solid engineering background allows me to approach data science from a practical, structured and product-oriented perspective.",
    "aboutContent_webDev": "Web developer with a background in Information Technology Engineering and experience in developing and maintaining internal web applications. I have worked with C#, .NET, and SQL Server building systems with roles, dashboards, and reports oriented to enterprise environments. Focused on developing functional, structured web solutions aligned with the organization's operational needs.",
    "aboutContent_dataAnalyst": "Data Analyst with a background in Information Technology Engineering and practical experience in data analysis within industrial environments. Experience analyzing production, warehouse, and supply chain data to identify recurring errors, reworks, and data quality issues. Ability to build dashboards and reports that allow detecting patterns, root causes, and improvement opportunities. Analytical and structured profile, focused on data-driven decision making.",
    "aboutContent_DataAnalysis": "Data Analyst with a background in Information Technology Engineering and practical experience in data analysis within industrial environments. Experience analyzing production, warehouse, and supply chain data to identify recurring errors, reworks, and data quality issues. Ability to build dashboards and reports that allow detecting patterns, root causes, and improvement opportunities. Analytical and structured profile, focused on data-driven decision making.",
